- Natural 1ct GIA F-VS1 Ideal Cushion Modified: **[$2,064](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25944037?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
- Natural 1ct GIA D-VVS1 Ideal Cushion Modified: **[$4,873](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29255833?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**

**→ The best entry point** for buyers who want maximum quality per dollar is the [GIA 1ct G-VS1 Ideal Cushion Modified at $1,891](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/23740863?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — GIA certification, G colour that reads as colourless in yellow or rose gold, VS1 clarity that is reliably eye-clean at 1ct, and Ideal cut. This stone in a rose gold pavé setting delivers the most popular 1ct cushion ring aesthetic for under $3,000 total. For buyers who want D colour on the certificate: the [GIA 1ct D-VVS1 Ideal at $4,873](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29255833?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the top-grade 1ct natural cushion available under $5,000.

