## 1ct Cushion Cut Lab Grown Diamond Ring

Lab-grown 1ct cushion diamonds are available at Blue Nile at prices well below $1,000 for IGI-certified stones. At 1ct, the lab saving versus natural ($1,891 natural entry) is approximately $1,200–$1,500 in absolute dollars — meaningful but not the $60,000–$78,000 gap that exists at 4ct–5ct. The more compelling lab comparison at 1ct is not "lab 1ct vs natural 1ct" but "lab 1.5ct vs natural 1ct" — because for the cost of a natural 1ct cushion, a lab upgrade to 1.5ct is achievable at a lower or comparable price.

