**The lab value argument at 1ct.** The [IGI 1.5ct E-VVS1 Ideal Cushion Modified lab at $1,854](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/25261211?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) costs effectively the same as a natural 1ct G-VS1 at $1,891 — but delivers 50% more face-up area (7.5mm × 7.5mm versus 6.5mm × 6.5mm), E colour, VVS1 clarity, and Ideal cut. This is the 1ct cushion lab value argument: not just "save money on the same stone" but "upgrade to a visually larger stone at the same price." The Modified Brilliant Split applies equally to lab cushions — always verify via HD video whether the lab stone is modified brilliant (crushed ice) or cushion brilliant (chunky facets).

